<s> McDermott International Inc. said its Babcock & Wilcox unit completed the sale of its Bailey Controls Operations to Finmeccanica S.p . A. for $ 295 million . </s>
<s> Finmeccanica is an Italian state-owned holding company with interests in the mechanical engineering industry . </s>
<s> Bailey Controls , based in Wickliffe , Ohio , makes computerized industrial controls systems . </s>
<s> It employs 2,700 people and has annual revenue of about $ 370 million . </s>
